### Session 1 - Health
GET http://localhost:8000/health

### Session 1 - Chat (non-stream)
POST http://localhost:8000/v1/chat/completions
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "model": "Qwen/Qwen2-1.5B-Instruct-AWQ",
  "messages": [
    {"role": "system", "content": "Responde en espanol."},
    {"role": "user", "content": "Define RAG en una frase corta."}
  ],
  "temperature": 0.2,
  "max_tokens": 80,
  "stream": false
}

### Session 1 - Chat (stream)
POST http://localhost:8000/v1/chat/completions
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "model": "Qwen/Qwen2-1.5B-Instruct-AWQ",
  "messages": [
    {"role": "user", "content": "Enumera tres ventajas de LLM local."}
  ],
  "stream": true
}

### Session 1 - Chat with Ollama model (when LLM_PROVIDER=ollama)
POST http://localhost:8000/v1/chat/completions
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "model": "qwen2:1.5b",
  "messages": [
    {"role": "user", "content": "Di hola en una frase."}
  ],
  "stream": false
}
